This is a kernel project. A small kernel is presented for students who is interested in kernel programming.

First you need djgpp (gcc Windows version) to compile .

Excute make && make install in kernel/.
g.bat invokes Makefile for you and generate NEW.bin ,which is the kernel image.

Use VMWare or Bochs to run New.bin , as floopy image.



